==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Foxiness
<hw>Fox"i*ness</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
state or quality of being foxy, or foxlike; craftiness;
shrewdness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The state of being foxed or discolored, as books;
decay; deterioration.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A coarse and sour taste in grapes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Foxish</ent>⟦br⟧
